dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows literary landmarks. "Based on John Speed's map, The Kingdome of Great Britaine and Ireland, from his 1611 atlas, Theatre of the Empire of Great Britaine." Includes table of "Shakespeare's plays with British settings" and col. ill. Insets: London -- Stretford upon Auen.
